[
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "chapter"
    },
    "innerText": "Nissaggiyakaṇḍaṃ"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "title"
    },
    "innerText": "1. Pattavaggo"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "1. Pattasannicayasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Paṭhamaṃ ",
      " uttānatthameva."
    ],
    "innerText": "Paṭhamaṃ uttānatthameva."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Pattasannicayasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "2. Akālacīvarasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Yaṃ attanā laddhaṃ, taṃ nissaggiyaṃ hotī"
      },
      "ti yaṃ cīvaraṃ bhājāpitāya attanā laddhaṃ, tameva nissaggiyaṃ hoti, taṃ vinayakammaṃ katvāpi attanā na labbhati. Tenāha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘nissaṭṭha’’"
      },
      "ntiādi. Tattha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "nissaṭṭhaṃ paṭilabhitvāpī"
      },
      "ti ‘‘ayyāya, dammī’’ti evaṃ nissaṭṭhaṃ paṭilabhitvāpi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Yathādāneyeva upanetabba"
      },
      "nti yathā dāyakehi dinnaṃ, tatheva upanetabbaṃ, akālacīvarapakkheyeva ṭhapetabbanti vuttaṃ hoti."
    ],
    "innerText": "Yaṃ attanā laddhaṃ, taṃ nissaggiyaṃ hotīti yaṃ cīvaraṃ bhājāpitāya attanā laddhaṃ, tameva nissaggiyaṃ hoti, taṃ vinayakammaṃ katvāpi attanā na labbhati. Tenāha ‘‘nissaṭṭha’’ntiādi. Tattha nissaṭṭhaṃ paṭilabhitvāpīti ‘‘ayyāya, dammī’’ti evaṃ nissaṭṭhaṃ paṭilabhitvāpi. Yathādāneyeva upanetabbanti yathā dāyakehi dinnaṃ, tatheva upanetabbaṃ, akālacīvarapakkheyeva ṭhapetabbanti vuttaṃ hoti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Akālacīvarasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "3. Cīvaraparivattanasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Meta"
      },
      "nti me etaṃ. Sakasaññāya gahitattā pācittiyañceva dukkaṭañca vuttaṃ, itarathā bhaṇḍagghena kāretabbaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "Metanti me etaṃ. Sakasaññāya gahitattā pācittiyañceva dukkaṭañca vuttaṃ, itarathā bhaṇḍagghena kāretabbaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Cīvaraparivattanasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "4. Aññaviññāpanasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paṭilābhenā"
      },
      "ti ",
      " paṭhamaviññattito ūnatarassāpi aññassa paṭilābhena."
    ],
    "innerText": "Paṭilābhenāti paṭhamaviññattito ūnatarassāpi aññassa paṭilābhena."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tasmiṃ appahonte puna taññevā"
      },
      "ti yaṃ paṭhamaṃ viññattaṃ, thokattā tasmiṃ appahonte puna taññeva viññāpentiyāti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Aññena"
      },
      "pi atthe ",
      " satī ti paṭhamaṃ viññattito aññenapi atthe sati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tena saddhiṃ aññañcā"
      },
      "ti yaṃ paṭhamaṃ viññattaṃ, tena saddhiṃ aññañca. Kiṃ vuttaṃ hoti? Sace paṭhamaṃ sappi viññattaṃ, ‘‘yamakaṃ pacitabba’’nti ca vejjena vuttattā telenāpi attho hoti. Tato ‘‘telenāpi me attho’’ti evamādinā aññañca viññāpentiyāti vuttaṃ hoti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ānisaṃsaṃ dassetvā"
      },
      "ti ‘‘sace kahāpaṇassa sappi ābhataṃ hoti, iminā mūlena dviguṇaṃ telaṃ labbhati, telenāpi ca idaṃ kiccaṃ nippajjati, tasmā telaṃ āharā’’ti evaṃ ānisaṃsaṃ dassetvā."
    ],
    "innerText": "Tasmiṃ appahonte puna taññevāti yaṃ paṭhamaṃ viññattaṃ, thokattā tasmiṃ appahonte puna taññeva viññāpentiyāti attho. Aññenapi atthe satī ti paṭhamaṃ viññattito aññenapi atthe sati. Tena saddhiṃ aññañcāti yaṃ paṭhamaṃ viññattaṃ, tena saddhiṃ aññañca. Kiṃ vuttaṃ hoti? Sace paṭhamaṃ sappi viññattaṃ, ‘‘yamakaṃ pacitabba’’nti ca vejjena vuttattā telenāpi attho hoti. Tato ‘‘telenāpi me attho’’ti evamādinā aññañca viññāpentiyāti vuttaṃ hoti. Ānisaṃsaṃ dassetvāti ‘‘sace kahāpaṇassa sappi ābhataṃ hoti, iminā mūlena dviguṇaṃ telaṃ labbhati, telenāpi ca idaṃ kiccaṃ nippajjati, tasmā telaṃ āharā’’ti evaṃ ānisaṃsaṃ dassetvā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Aññaviññāpanasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "5. Aññacetāpanasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tato aññaṃ cetāpeyyā"
      },
      "ti paṭhamaṃ cetāpitato yaṃ kiñci aññaṃ cetāpeyya."
    ],
    "innerText": "Tato aññaṃ cetāpeyyāti paṭhamaṃ cetāpitato yaṃ kiñci aññaṃ cetāpeyya."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Aññacetāpanasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "6. Paṭhamasaṅghikacetāpanasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Aññassatthāya dinnenā"
      },
      "ti yaṃ cetāpeti, tato aññassatthāya dinnena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Aññuddisikenā"
      },
      "ti purimassevatthadīpanaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "Aññassatthāya dinnenāti yaṃ cetāpeti, tato aññassatthāya dinnena. Aññuddisikenāti purimassevatthadīpanaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sesakaṃ upanentiyā"
      },
      "ti yadatthāya dinno, taṃ cetāpetvā avasesaṃ aññassatthāya upanentiyā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sāmike apaloketvā"
      },
      "ti dāyake āpucchitvā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Evarūpāsū āpadāsu upanentīna"
      },
      "nti evarūpesu upaddavesu aññassa yassa kassaci atthāya upanentīnaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "Sesakaṃ upanentiyāti yadatthāya dinno, taṃ cetāpetvā avasesaṃ aññassatthāya upanentiyā. Sāmike apaloketvāti dāyake āpucchitvā. Evarūpāsū āpadāsu upanentīnanti evarūpesu upaddavesu aññassa yassa kassaci atthāya upanentīnaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Paṭhamasaṅghikacetāpanasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "7. Dutiyasaṅghikacetāpanasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Na ",
      " kevalaṃ teneva parikkhārenāti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘sayaṃ yācitakenāpī’’"
      },
      "ti. Vuttañhetaṃ pāḷiyaṃ ‘‘bhikkhuniyo tena ca parikkhārena sayampi yācitvā bhesajjaṃ cetāpetvā paribhuñjiṃsū’’ti (pāci. 763). Mātikāyaṃ pana gamyamānattā pi-saddo nappayutto. Gamyamānatthassa hi saddassa payogaṃ pati kāmacāroti yutti."
    ],
    "innerText": "Na kevalaṃ teneva parikkhārenāti āha ‘‘sayaṃ yācitakenāpī’’ti. Vuttañhetaṃ pāḷiyaṃ ‘‘bhikkhuniyo tena ca parikkhārena sayampi yācitvā bhesajjaṃ cetāpetvā paribhuñjiṃsū’’ti (pāci. 763). Mātikāyaṃ pana gamyamānattā pi-saddo nappayutto. Gamyamānatthassa hi saddassa payogaṃ pati kāmacāroti yutti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Dutiyasaṅghikacetāpanasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "8-9-10. Paṭhamagaṇikacetāpanādisikkhāpadavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "innerText": "Aṭṭhamanavamadasamāni uttānatthāneva."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Paṭhamagaṇikacetāpanādisikkhāpadavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Pattavaggo paṭhamo."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "title"
    },
    "innerText": "2. Cīvaravaggo"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "11. Garupāvuraṇasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Yasmā pavāritaṭṭhāne viññatti nāma na paṭisedhetabbā, tasmā bhagavā dhammanimantanavasena pavāritaṭṭhāne ‘‘vadethāyye, yenattho’’ti (sārattha. ṭī. pācittiya 3.784) vuttāya catukkaṃsaparamaṃ viññāpetabbanti paricchedaṃ dassetīti veditabbaṃ. Teneva ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘cetāpetabbanti ṭhapetvā sahadhammike ca ñātakappavārite ca aññena kismiñcideva guṇe parituṭṭhena ‘vadethāyye, yenattho’ti vuttāya viññāpetabba’’"
      },
      "nti vuttaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Rājāna"
      },
      "nti pasenadikosalarājānaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "Yasmā pavāritaṭṭhāne viññatti nāma na paṭisedhetabbā, tasmā bhagavā dhammanimantanavasena pavāritaṭṭhāne ‘‘vadethāyye, yenattho’’ti (sārattha. ṭī. pācittiya 3.784) vuttāya catukkaṃsaparamaṃ viññāpetabbanti paricchedaṃ dassetīti veditabbaṃ. Teneva ‘‘cetāpetabbanti ṭhapetvā sahadhammike ca ñātakappavārite ca aññena kismiñcideva guṇe parituṭṭhena ‘vadethāyye, yenattho’ti vuttāya viññāpetabba’’nti vuttaṃ. Rājānanti pasenadikosalarājānaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Garupāvuraṇasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "12. Lahupāvuraṇasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Dutiyaṃ ",
      " uttānatthameva."
    ],
    "innerText": "Dutiyaṃ uttānatthameva."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Lahupāvuraṇasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Cīvaravaggo dutiyo."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Iti kaṅkhāvitaraṇiyā pātimokkhavaṇṇanāya"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Vinayatthamañjūsāyaṃ līnatthappakāsaniyaṃ"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Bhikkhunipātimokkhe nissaggiyavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  }
]